_:N6f90abcfd96f44db920732e4c9825126 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Boris Johnson was Prime Minister from 24 July 2019 to 6 September 2022. He was previously Foreign Secretary from 13 July 2016 to 9 July 2018.</p>\n\n<p>He was Conservative MP for Uxbridge and South Ruislip from May 2015 to June 2023. Previously he was the MP for Henley from June 2001 to June 2008.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
